title: Darkest Dungeon Build 11907
description:
Title: Darkest Dungeon
Genre: Indie, RPG, Strategy, Early Access
Developer: Red Hook Studios 
Publisher: Red Hook Studios	
Release Date: 3 Feb, 2015


Changes #11907

- Diseases should happen less off of CRITs. 
- Stall System 
Stress Penalty should no longer occur if there is a DOT applied that will be lethal that turn.
Tweaked Stall Mechanics for Octotanks (Should give players more time to handle them)

Bug Fixes 
- No longer able to spam transform on the Abomination in combat 
- Click on Crest/Retreat Flag no longer makes your party backpedal 
- Provisioning issues

Cahnges #11887 see complete notes here:  
http://www.darkestdungeon.com/inhuman-bondage-patch-notes/
